1
00:00:07,890 --> 00:00:09,431
{\ あ、なんで今のは？ }
What was that just now?

2
00:00:11,718 --> 00:00:13,013
{\ どうしたの、ユリィ？ }
What happened, Yurii?

3
00:00:13,409 --> 00:00:17,764
{\ 人が、王税の人の命が… }
Many people... Many people suddenly...

4
00:00:17,980 --> 00:00:21,231
{\ 一瞬で殺されたの… }
{\ まさか、アドモニッシャー! }
They were killed?
Could it have been the Admonisher?

5
00:00:23,956 --> 00:00:29,479
{\ 殺されたなどということがねぇが }
They were not simply killed... they were annihilated!

6
00:00:29,839 --> 00:00:31,839
{\ 後ろ、総めっさせられた! }
Annihilated?

7
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:35,339
{\ さっきの爆発は南の方からしたぜ }
Where did this happen!?

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:38,788
{\ 総めっちゃ… }
The explosion came from the south.

9
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:41,475
{\ かなり遠いようだったが }
It seemed pretty far away, though.

10
00:00:41,901 --> 00:00:43,691
{\ 南、て、 }
South?

11
00:00:44,050 --> 00:00:46,059
{\ ペルメンティアの方 }
That's in the direction of Felmentia...